      "content": "i feel like im just spinning my wheels. every time i think i finally got a handle on things, i mess it up. new job, then i lose it. trying to stay sober, then i crash. it's like i'm stuck in this shitty loop and no matter how hard i fight, i just end up back at zero. it never actually changes.",
